name: Building Capillaries
description:
The trees all look like veins and capillaries to me when contrasted against a cloudy sky. And my thoughts immediately go to all the varied lives and perspectives of the people living these apartment buildings. Growing up in the oldest co-op building complex in the country, you can’t help but feel connected to the people who have that shared experience.

3840x2160 JPEG

Photo by Jason Charnick
Taken in the Bronx, NY, USA
